🔥 BBQ just got sweeter! 🔥
Say aloha to dessert done right our Self BBQ Bento with a S’MORES setup! 🍫🔥🍡 

We're excited to announce our partnership with Diamond Bakery. Every s'mores box comes with the classic graham crackers from @diamondbakeryhawaii 

Roast your own marshmallows tableside, stack ‘em high with melty chocolate and Diamond Bakery crispy graham crackers, and enjoy the ultimate island-style treat with a twist. 🤙

Whether you’re sharing with your ohana or treating yourself, this is the perfect way to end your bento experience on a high (and gooey) note. 🍢

Meet the snack box that brings the islands to your doorstep! 🌴

The Aloha Cravings Box is packed with sweet, salty, and ʻono local favorites, from seaweed snacks and tropical gummies to buttery toffee cookies, passion fruit chocolate, and even Hawaiian soda. 

Whether you're sending a taste of Hawai‘i to someone you love or stocking up for your next event, this box is all about bold flavors, bright packaging, and feel good vibes from across the islands.
